{"id":56768,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/04/中国股市午盘转跌-地产股拖累大盘/","date":"2010-04-06T14:30:05Z","modified":"2010-04-06T18:23:09Z","title":"中国股市午盘转跌 地产股拖累大盘","content":"<p><span></span></p>\n<div style=\"float:left;width:28px;color:#c74b15;border:0px solid #000000;margin:0px 0px 0px 0px;padding:0px 0px 0px 0px;line-height:140%;font-size:28px;font-weight:bolder\">中</div>\n<p>国股市周二午盘转跌，政策风险担忧令地产股拖累大盘，午后或窄幅波动。上证综指前市高开后逐步走低，午盘跌0.06%，报3156.21点；成交人民币855亿元，较上周五略微放大3%。</p>\n<p>群益证券分析师认为，地产股是拖累大盘的主要因素，因新华社评论引发市场对地产政策进一步收紧的担忧；预计上证综指午后将在3150点附近整理，量能维持预示短线大幅调整可能性较小。</p>\n<p>盘面看，地产股领跌，保利地产(600048)午盘跌3.40%；物联网概念、造船、铁路建设、保险等板块走低。重庆板块和煤炭股涨幅靠前；化纤、创业板股多活跃。深证成指午盘跌0.39%，报12717.81点。</p>\n<div style=\"border-bottom:1px #ccc solid;padding-bottom:5px;padding-top:14px;margin-bottom:8px\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><img src=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100406/../img/more_arrows.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"10\" width=\"5\"> 本文涉及股票或公司</span></div>\n<div style=\"font-size:14px\">\n<div style=\"background-color:EEF2F4;padding:8px\">\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:8px;height:120px\"><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"color:0066cc\" href=\"http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20100406/../stocksearch.asp?KeyWord=600048.SH&amp;chinesename=%E4%BF%9D%E5%88%A9%E6%88%BF%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%A7%EF%BC%88%E9%9B%86%E5%9B%A2%EF%BC%89%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%EF%BC%88%E7%AE%80%E7%A7%B0%EF%BC%9A%E4%BF%9D%E5%88%A9%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%A7%EF%BC%89&amp;englishname=Poly%20Real%20Estate%20Group%20Co.&amp;country=%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86&amp;exchange=%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%AF%81%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80&amp;symbol=600048\">保利房地产（集团）股份有限公司（简称：保利地产）</a></b><br />英文名称：Poly Real Estate Group Co.<br />总部地点：中国大陆<br />上市地点：上海证交所<br />股票代码：600048</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><iframe src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~ah/f/750jserb5tdifd602qjvu6ia28/300/250?ca=1&amp;fh=280#http%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Fgb%2F20100406%2Fmkt114339.asp%3Fsource%3Drss\" width=\"100%\" height=\"280\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\